Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spellamiso. A perennial plant\Nfrom the Aoshidare family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you steam the roots and dry them,\Nit can lower fevers and alleviate pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's time to open the shop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...my own path...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...my own story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had my wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I would keep writing my own path like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:40.09,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 1: Encounter...\NChanging the Color of Fate"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror, Mirror on the wall,\Nwho's the fairest girl in the land?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sakaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an informant from town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's telling me everything as he sees it,\Nso he might as well be a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, please do not joke around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You too! Don't just stand there!\NTell me your information!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know who the most beautiful\Ngirl in the kingdom of Tanbarun is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, what about {\i1}that{\i0} girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a girl born with exceptionally\Nrare red hair, as red as an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Shirayuki, Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to take your medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshi, feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is the medicine for you, Kino, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came to let my eyes\Nrest on your beautiful hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But since you're here,\NI'll prepare some more medicine for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a hold of some good medicinal herbs,\Nso please take some with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a fine herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish your dead grandparents could see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Kino--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered! I left the stove on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can just bring it to her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget someth--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Raj's... concubine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in other words, a mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he'd want a town girl\Nlike me because of the color of my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be an embarrassment to the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That Prince Raj has taken a liking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you must formally present\Nyourself to the castle tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dress yourself up tonight while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For Kino, something to relieve the pain in her back\Nand stop the inflammation of her respiratory tract.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At Yuri's place, the father and\Nbaby were coming down with a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Tanbarun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Is anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just go in without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's getting dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm starting to get hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, Kiki! I'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're going from a place like that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you injured? Did you hit your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's one plus one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who're you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Mitsuhide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was that your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki! You, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, so deep in the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, I just followed a road without many\Npeople in the middle of running away, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have strange hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, people often tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right arm... It's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an herbalist. I have a\Npoultice you can use if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be poison or something. How can I\Nuse it if someone gives it to me all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm a dwarf or something.\NI'm not going to trust someone so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I've no business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand, then get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what he said {\i1}was{\i0} true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there are arrogant people everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't make it\Na habit to carry poison around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She got you, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. My name's Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was half your fault that I missed\Nmy landing in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an unoccupied house,\Nbut we hang out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one losing at\Nchess over there is Mitsuhide,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the one winning easily is Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, how can you say for sure\Nthat I'm losing without even looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're good at this, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that I'm an herbalist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why did an herbalist\Nlike you run away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why did you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be dishonorable as a gentleman to allow\Nan injured girl to go into the woods alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I got used to the mountains and\Nforests while studying to be an herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The time and air flow differently\Nfrom the town here, and it feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were your honest feelings just now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a strand that's longer than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I must've missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Zen. Will you cut it off for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I can't cut a woman's hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does cutting off your long hair have something\Nto do with why you ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell me the reason, I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You were told to become his concubine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,By a famous rich boy who learned to speak\Nin the red-light district and ate silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought red hair was unusual\Nand wanted to keep it by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I did as he said, it'd be like he was\Nbuying an apple at the fruit seller's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shirayuki--\N--That's why I thought I'd\Nhave him tire of it little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and left my hair behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a great decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job getting away from that lowlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's your precious red.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious red?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Red is supposed to be the color of fate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's annoying now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it might connect to something\Ngood when you least expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You have an amazing way of thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem suspicious after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but Zen seems to really like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the ribbon I tied my hair in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were from Tanbarun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who sent this came all the\Nway to the border to get you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be a very spiteful gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this matter so serious that\Nyou had to run across the border?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of who he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first prince of Tanbarun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Raj!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That... idiot... prince... huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a huge idiot that rumors\Neven spread to the neighboring countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of who he is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably had people looking\Nthrough all the border crossing records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He would go that far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something he wants,\Nhe probably already counts it as his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means caging it? No way, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to go bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This red is no good anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so impolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that, Zen. You should get it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What're ya--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should either talk or eat. Don't do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't call you. Stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said something stupid. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki. You shouldn't eat that apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, Mitsuhide... Don't get... mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's poisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have an antidote?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. I can't prepare one with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Miss Shirayuki was\Nnot the one who ate the apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry. A certain person has the antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you will come with me quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's you? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The red hair you left behind was real, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what about the antidote for my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Miss Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is a frightening place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I courted you and\Nyou ran away has made me a laughingstock
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in town and in the royal palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, thanks to that,\Npublic opinion of me has plunged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the rumors all\Nagree that it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in order to clear my good name,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you ask to be my concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're just a lowly town girl,\NI didn't want to cause a woman embarrassment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so this is the solution I painstakingly came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Am I hearing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, more importantly, what about the antidote?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I could get the\Nantidote for my friend, Prince Raj?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. If you just nod your head,\NI will have it delivered, promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:17:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, would you rather\NI have this delivered instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Red is supposed to be the color of fate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's annoying now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it might connect to something\Ngood when you least expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I... to that person who gave me those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, now that I know you\Nare so easy on the eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not want you to be far from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Raj. Take me as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I object!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please stop retching such\Ndirty jokes that sully that girl's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shirayuki. Tie this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, before that, what about your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been building up an immunity to\Npoison slowly in case I ever got poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}you{\i0} are the man who was poisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning on making Miss Shirayuki\Nimmobile and taking her home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one who\Nhanded over those apples, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch how you speak to me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a big difference\Nbetween our social status!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, first prince of Tanbarun,\NPrince Raj Schenazade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is annoying,\Nbut let me introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That crest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the second prince of the\Nkingdom of Clarines, Zen Wisteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Second...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Z-Zen, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's one plus one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never thought I'd be poisoned by a\Nprince from a neighboring kingdom, Prince Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You... You have\Nno proof that I have the poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can test that in an official inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, why don't have a trade, idiot prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want your\Nfoolish actions to be made public,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,then swear you will never approach\NShirayuki again or say her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know Shirayuki--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just swore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, I'm sure you have\Na ton of things to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to complain,\Nyou should do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Raj. This is hoping you get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it looks like you're\Nso surprised you can't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...hurry up and give the antidote to Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I only became poison to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was poisoned\Nby an apple, and you're red?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's not something\Nyou need to apologize for, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen ate it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, Mitsuhide, and I should\Nhave been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide carried on like he would die\Nif Zen died and got all teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Next time, if I get fruit,\NI'll have Mitsuhide peel it before I eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that what we were talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, do you remember\Nwhat I said in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, I hope the fact that\Nwe're here together right now is fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in the forest you were\Nheading toward on your journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,where we met and tried to protect each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether that's poison\Nthat's only found in this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or connections for the future\Nis something you can decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay for me to decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! {\i1}I'm{\i0} deciding {\i1}my{\i0} own fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After you decide, it's up to you whether\Nor not you follow that path, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:21:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do have an amazing way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not how I think, it's how I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's literally my own story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had my wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on the path in front of us after this encounter,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the sound of pages turning in this story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,will echo like the sound of\Nfootsteps one on top of the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.94,0:24:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I could finally see you, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarines is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Shirayuki's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I decided to come to this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:19.97,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 2: Following the Sound of Your Heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you decide to stop running, Red?
